'''尼爾·格雷'''（Neil Gray，{{bd|1986年|3月16日}}）是一位[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]政治人物，他的黨籍是[[蘇格蘭民族黨|蘇格蘭民族黨]]。自2015年開始，他擔任[[艾迪爾與蕭特_(英國國會選區)|艾迪爾與蕭特]]選區選出的國會議員<ref>{{cite web|title=Airdrie & Shotts Parliamentary constituency|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/S14000003|website=Election 2015 Results|publisher=BBC|accessdate=8 May 2015|archive-date=2016-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160214062138/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/S14000003|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他出生並成長在[[奧克尼|奧克尼]]。

==谴责中国政府==
2020年9月8日在[[英国工党|工党]][[希柏恩·麦克唐纳|希柏恩·麦克唐纳]]的协调下，与包括[[英国保守党|英国保守党]]外交事务委员会主席[[托马斯·图根达特|托马斯·图根达特]]、[[自由民主党_(英国)|自由民主党]]领袖[[爱德·戴维|爱德·戴维]]，以及{{le|英国绿党|Green Party (UK)}}、[[苏格兰民族党|苏格兰民族党]]和[[威尔士党|威尔士党]]在内的130多名议员给中国驻英大使[[刘晓明|刘晓明]]写信，联名谴责中国政府[[新疆再教育营|针对新疆维吾尔穆斯林的行为]]。<ref>{{cite news |author1=法广 |title=英国近百名议员联名谴责中共针对新疆维吾尔穆斯林的行为 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200909-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%AE%E5%91%98%E8%81%94%E5%90%8D%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E7%A9%86%E6%96%AF%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA |accessdate=2020-09-29 |agency=RFI |date=2020-09-10 |archive-date=2020-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910225118/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200909-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%AE%E5%91%98%E8%81%94%E5%90%8D%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E7%A9%86%E6%96%AF%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=DAVID ALTON |title=Led by Siobhain McDonagh MP, 130 parliamentarians have today written to the Chinese Ambassador to the UK condemning treatment of Uyghur people in Xinjiang |url=https://davidalton.net/2020/09/08/led-by-siobhain-mcdonagh-mp-130-parliamentarians-have-today-written-to-the-chinese-ambassador-to-the-uk-condemning-treatment-of-uyghur-people-in-xinjiang/ |accessdate=2020-09-29 |date=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2020-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917001800/https://davidalton.net/2020/09/08/led-by-siobhain-mcdonagh-mp-130-parliamentarians-have-today-written-to-the-chinese-ambassador-to-the-uk-condemning-treatment-of-uyghur-people-in-xinjiang/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
